Reporter refactor: - created a singleton "reporter" class that enables reports to any combination of: System.out JTextArea (in this UI) micromanager logs
Which of the three is determined by flags. Passing the JTextArea as a parameter is removed from many constructors (can be seen as bad practice, but we'll see)
added lots more text outputs for debugging
meta Store now has x-dimensions, y-dimensions, and bitdepth that are callable as getters necessary for py4j to retrieve primitives instead of java objects
fixed classloder problem that prevented python implementing java interface
cleaned up ramdisk implmementation cleaned up temp path setup
mouse press event added to temp file selection fixed some pathing for temp file
completed builder and parambuilder plus tests
completed tests refactored UI and py4j entry point
changes to data queues tests for data queues groundwork for concurrent testing
added tests for concurrency using latches
refactor: adjusted data passed to datastoreEventsThread refactor: UI changes refactor: temp file path management
